depositZircuit().details: Only delegate callable on Liquidity, by Governance

withdrawZircuit().details: Only delegate callable on Liquidity, Governance and Guardians (for emergency)

depositZircuit().notice: deposit all WEETH funds to Zircuit and sets approved allowance to max uint256.

withdrawZircuit().notice: withdraw all WEETH funds from Zircuit and sets approved allowance to 0.
